des: CCV Stars North Phoenix Baseball games schedule by next game. Game times, ballfield, and opponent teams are provided. No personal information is being used within this skill and is nothing is being collected or saved. Teams are now using three fields. Providing this new skill technology as simple aid to help team parents find their ballfield when they arrive at the games. Say your coach or team's name to hear the next game time, field color, and opponent your team is playing.
